  "text": "In other words, we need to better understand how the action of the human species has modified and still modifies ecosystems and other species and how past human decisions may have affected the way we interact with plants in the present (see examples of approaches in [CITATION_1] . Research guided by this approach can reveal how past human decisions affect the evolution of plant-based knowledge systems (PBKS).",
